<h2>Create a new Ingredient:</h2>
<%= form_for(@ingredient) do |f|%>
    <label>Enter the name:</label>
    <%= f.text_field :name %><br>

    <label>Type:</label>
    <%= f.text_field :ingredient_type %><br>
    The ingredient types are "Main ingredient" and "Special ingredient".
    Examples of main ingredients are Rum, Whiskey, Vermouth, and Lemon Juice.
    Examples of special ingredients are "2 dashes of bitters" or "2 fresh mint leaves" or "Salt".
    <br>

    <%= f.submit %>
<% end %>
